---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import paintbrush from "../assets/images/paintbrush-canvas.png";
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us" height={2279}>
  <section class="about-story">
    <div class="copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">OUR STORY</p>
      <h1 class="page-title">About HeArt to Heart</h1>
      <h2 class="serif">Why “HeArt to Heart”?</h2>
      <p>
        “Heart” and “Art.” True connection happens when we share our true hearts
        through the language of art. That's the journey we're on: from one heart
        to another.
      </p>
      <h2 class="serif">My “Why”</h2>
      <p>
        I started this because I often had feelings I couldn't name. Sometimes,
        words felt too small, too limiting. I felt confused, frustrated, and
        alone. Then, I discovered that putting a color to my mood, or moving to
        music, gave those feelings a home. It was a quiet revolution inside me.
        I wanted to build a bridge so others might find that path, too.
      </p>
      <h2 class="serif">From School Club to This Website</h2>
      <p>
        HeArt to Heart began in my school—a small group of friends sharing art
        activities. Seeing how a simple exercise could light up someone's eyes
        made me dream bigger. This website is that dream: to extend our circle
        beyond the classroom walls.
      </p>
    </div>
    <img src={paintbrush.src} alt="A paintbrush covered in bright paint" />
  </section>

  <section class="values soft-panel">
    <blockquote class="serif">“Art is not a profession, but a way of life.”</blockquote>
    <div class="value-grid">
      <article>
        <h3>Explore</h3>
        <p>Digging out the aesthetic moments hidden in daily life, redefining the ordinary.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h3>Heal</h3>
        <p>Relieving anxiety and finding inner peace and strength through creation and observation.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h3>Connect</h3>
        <p>Building a warm community where every heart that loves art can meet.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-story {
    position: absolute;
    top: 161px;
    left: 112px;
    display: grid;
    width: 1216px;
    grid-template-columns: 575px 568px;
    gap: 73px;
  }

  .copy h1 {
    margin: 33px 0 37px;
    font-size: 52px;
    line-height: 69px;
  }

  .copy h2 {
    margin: 24px 0 10px;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .copy p:not(.eyebrow) {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    line-height: 23px;
  }

  .about-story img {
    width: 568px;
    height: 806px;
    margin-top: 44px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    object-fit: cover;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }

  .values {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1211px;
    left: 112px;
    width: 1216px;
    height: 452px;
    padding: 120px 145px 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  blockquote {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .value-grid {
    display: grid;
    margin-top: 60px;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 65px;
  }

  h3 {
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .value-grid p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    line-height: 20px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1439px) {
    .about-story,
    .values {
      position: relative;
      top: auto;
      left: auto;
      width: auto;
      height: auto;
      margin: 0 var(--page-gutter);
    }

    .about-story {
      padding: var(--section-gap) 0;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: clamp(40px, 7vw, 72px);
    }

    .copy h1 {
      margin: 28px 0 34px;
    }

    .about-story img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      margin-top: 0;
      aspect-ratio: 568 / 806;
    }

    .values {
      margin-bottom: var(--section-gap);
      padding: clamp(64px, 9vw, 100px) clamp(28px, 8vw, 100px);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .about-story,
    .value-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-story img {
      max-height: 620px;
    }

    .values {
      text-align: left;
    }

    .value-grid {
      gap: 36px;
    }
  }
</style>
